{
  "stem": "14387.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "None of my sisters-in-law worked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were-- how many sisters-in-law were there?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Half a dozen of us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we just kept the house, kept the place going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as refugees started to cross the border, they all knew-- it became known-- they used to go, say, well, how are we going to cross into-- well, what are we going to do when we get there?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it became known that you go to the Isaksens.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the refugees used to come to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a large apartment we had-- well, we were 21 people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to sleep on the floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they used to come to us, and we would put everybody up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would put them on the floor, and they would stay with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were-- oh, dozens of people every day at our house, at our apartment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we became well-known for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Go to the-- go to the Isaksens.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Norway.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Norway.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Jewish-- Jewish people from Norway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of them, there were a couple that got shot on the border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember one fellow that was staying with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, let me tell you something-- what happened with these Norwegian refugees.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were all naive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were all naive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They came to Stockholm, and at that time, the Germans were not doing anything to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course we kept, you know-- because In Stockholm, you were allowed to use a shortwave radio.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we could know what was going on in the rest of the world.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Germans were not doing anything to the Norwegian Jews, and they were naive enough to think that it would continue that way.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What-- and so, they wanted to go back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Remember, these were all fairly prosperous people.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
